OL,6,FThe parents of a girl who was hit by a
OL,7,Fcar while waiting at a bus stop have
OL,8,Fcriticised the "appalling" police
OL,9,Finvestigation into her death.
OL,11,FKatelyn Dawson, who was 15, died when
OL,12,Fa BMW being driven by 57-year-old
OL,13,FRichard Brooke collided with a bus
OL,14,Fstop on Wakefield Road, Moldgreen,
OL,15,FHuddersfield, on 10 January 2018.
OL,17,FRecording a narrative verdict
OL,18,Ffollowing , coroner Martin Fleming
OL,19,Fdescribed the situation as
OL,20,F"despairingly hard" for the family.
