OL,6,FBut in a statement outside court
OL,7,Ffollowing the inquest, Katelyn's
OL,8,Fparents said the coroner had to reach
OL,9,Fa conclusion in the face of the
OL,10,F"limitations of the evidence
OL,11,Fpresented" by police.
OL,13,FThey said: "What we cannot understand
OL,14,For accept is the appalling way in
OL,15,Fwhich Katelyn's death has been
OL,16,Finvestigated by West Yorkshire Police.
