OL,6,F"After two investigations, there was
OL,7,Fstill crucial evidence detailed at the
OL,8,Finquest that the police had not looked
OL,9,Finto properly. West Yorkshire Police
OL,10,Ffailed Katelyn and this is something
OL,11,Fthat will haunt us for the rest of our
OL,12,Flives."
OL,14,F'All the evidence was shared'JIn
OL,15,Fresponse a West Yorkshire Police
OL,16,Fspokesperson said Katelyn's death was
OL,17,F"clearly a dreadful incident".
