OL,6,FThey added: "An investigation of the
OL,7,Fcircumstances of the collision was
OL,8,Fundertaken over the course of a number
OL,9,Fof months by officers from the major
OL,10,Fcollision enquiry team. The
OL,11,Finvestigation was also subject of a
OL,12,Ffurther separate review at the
OL,13,Ffamily's request.
OL,15,F"All evidence from the original
OL,16,Finvestigation and the subsequent
OL,17,Freview was presented to the Crown
OL,18,FProsecution Service for consideration.
