OL,6,FAfter dropping his son off at school,
OL,7,Fhe described a sensation of "falling
OL,8,Fforwards" and fearing as he lost
OL,9,Fconsciousness and veered into the bus
OL,10,Fstop.
OL,12,FThere was no evidence to suggest Mr
OL,13,FBrooke was driving erratically
OL,14,Fbeforehand, Mr Fleming said.
OL,16,FHe described Katelyn, who attended
OL,17,FShelley College in Huddersfield, as a
OL,18,F"much-loved daughter, sister and
OL,19,Fgranddaughter who had so much to live
OL,20,Ffor" and a "beautiful young lady with
OL,21,Fwarmth and compassion".
